Nutrient-Dense Fats​ provide essential Omega-3 that promote healthy skin, a lustrous coat, and support strong bones and joints for your pet's overall vitality.​ Low-temperature processing preserves B vitamins, calcium, and phosphorus—aiding metabolism, bone strength, and vision

Versatile for Training & Mealtime: Our highly palatable chicken dog treats are perfect for training rewards, standalone snacks, or as a delicious meal topper. Easily break them into smaller pieces for training or crumble over kibble to add a burst of flavor and nutrition to your pet’s regular meals, making every feeding interaction enjoyable

Suitable for All Dogs & Cats: Ideal for carnivorous pets of all ages, breeds, and sizes, from playful puppies and kittens to senior companions. Lilsnoots' simple freeze-dried chicken treats support overall well-being and are conveniently packaged for freshness, offering great value for everyday use in multi-pet households or for long-lasting enjoyment

short_description: THE FIRST ORGANIC SINGLE INGREDIENT TREATS – Our line of organic treats are the first single ingredient organic treats on the market. ORGANIC 100% GRASS FED AND FINISHED BEEF LIVER, JUST ONE INGREDIENT - Our treats are excellent for dogs with allergies, sensitive stomachs, diabetes, or dietary requirements. These treats are grain-free, gluten-free, and low fat-diet approved. Organic Beef avoids dangerous chemicals and pesticides to have the most stomach friendly functional treats. Grass Fed & Finished Beef is shown to have 33% less fat, 11% higher protein, and up to 5 times as much Omega 3s. We demand the absolute best quality beef- no additives, no funny business, no nonsense.

WHY 100% GRASS FED BEEF LIVER - Beef Liver is a densely packed healthy nutrient powerhouse. Liver has been shown to have 67% less fat, 16 times the Vitamin D, and 23 times the calcium of traditional beef muscle meat. We want our beef liver to be the most nutrient dense possible therefore we opt for pasture raised organic 100% grass fed & finished beef that are able to get exercise resulting in lower fat, higher protein, and more Omega 3s than grain fed beef.

HEALTHY SKIN & COAT - Beef liver is a natural source of nutrients that contain essential fatty acids like Omega 3, Omega 6, Taurine, Calcium, Zinc, and Vitamins A, and D. These nutrients work together to create healthier skin and shinier coats that shed less.

SUSTAINABLY SOURCED AND MADE IN THE USA: Our treats are sustainably sourced, organic, and human grade. They are made in the US at our organic certified facility to ensure human grade quality. Freeze drying is shown to be the best way to preserve natural nutrients with over 61% more nutrients retained relative to dehydration or cooking. Our mission is to ensure only the freshest, healthiest, and best quality ingredients to make A BETTER TREAT
